#
#  fang distinctive features:
#    - WRAPPER PATTERN — fang doesn't replace cobra; it WRAPS
#      `cobra.Command.Execute()` with a richer entry point that
#      adds styling, error formatting, signal handling, and meta-
#      commands (manpage/completion generation)
#    - CHARM BRACELET STYLING — uses lipgloss internally to
#      render help text, usage lines, error messages, and version
#      output with consistent Charm Bracelet color scheme (cyan
#      headings, magenta required-flag indicators, gray-on-bg
