#    - SIGNAL CHAINING — multiple signals can be wired with
#      `fang.WithNotifySignal(os.Interrupt, syscall.SIGTERM)`
#      for daemon-mode CLIs
#    - INSPIRED BY Charm Bracelet's internal tools (gum/glow/
#      freeze/vhs/skate) which all share a common entry pattern
#      — fang externalizes that pattern as a reusable library
