#  R431 Go peterbourgon/ff/v3/ffcli, R435 Go posener/complete,
#  R438 Go voxelbrain/goptions, R441 Go muesli/coral
#  (CHARMBRACELET CO-FOUNDER's other Go CLI library — coral is
