#
#  Examples:
#    tldx hello world                                    # Check hello.com, world.com (default TLDs)
#    tldx -t com,io,ai hello                             # Check hello.com, hello.io, hello.ai
#    tldx -p get,my -s ify hello                         # gethelloify.com, myhelloify.com, ...
